{"tid":1014841,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Jan Jan 串掦專門店 食評","createTime":"2019-02-09T13:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T06:28:06.000Z","uid":21545,"like":14,"dislike":103,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3b5b4d67065284fd657f46ae662dcc2b83b3948b","tid":1014841,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:42:49.000Z","msg":"新年逗完利是當然要食返餐好 所以帶埋阿媽去食日式串炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c0TW7AG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0TW7AG.png&h=d180173e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGULgt3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwGULgt3.png&h=8ac34dca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oxYj5np.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoxYj5np.png&h=b71f040b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjviBt6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjviBt6.png&h=5475852e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnJwb2r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnJwb2r.png&h=2cbed70d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgJDBt8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgJDBt8.png&h=ed023e6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pSwWub.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pSwWub.png&h=cf63780c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/09/211919_deba57e2e207e0bc37ad6a494217ef0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F09%2F211919_deba57e2e207e0bc37ad6a494217ef0c.png&h=c7aa9701&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/09/211924_79db747595c822b87839126eda8618de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F09%2F211924_79db747595c822b87839126eda8618de.png&h=4cdcfe45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/09/211926_c78391178101bf8f12c057f75d8bc374.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F09%2F211926_c78391178101bf8f12c057f75d8bc374.png&h=44b3cb21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲串炸係即叫即炸新鮮熱辣又好味 款式有大路又有創新 例如炸鴨胸拼他他醬 炸蘋果 同 炸咖哩飯咁 整體味道唔錯 口感夠脆 醬汁酸甜有序<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除串炸之外 仲有小食 串燒同主食 <br />\n<br />\n小食 叫咗一個燒明太子 不過不失 <br />\n高湯雞蛋卷 多汁又嫩 充滿昆布高湯味 <br />\n<br />\n串燒叫咗 一串燒牛脷 冇過火夠嫩 有油香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主食 豚肉飯卷 同 燒飯糰 香而不乾 調味適中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n茶泡飯 好鹹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n侍應有禮 服務殷勤 值得一讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n評分：8/10<br />\n<br />\n價錢：埋單$640 兩個人食 一串大概$30 主食同小食就$40-50一碟 飲品$25/杯 <br />\n<br />\n總結：味道唔錯 但小貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf9ac97297d5c482fce7d229aefe23d0abff8ca","tid":1014841,"uid":192730,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"走啦"},{"pid":"ad0861a126947436f71083fa4c04ed3dc2a5e188","tid":1014841,"uid":45213,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:43:44.000Z","msg":"殺人放火金腰帶!"},{"pid":"8b05c946d7447a17ad63c0c82a06eceb6e0e2c0b","tid":1014841,"uid":71508,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"640<br />\nCls<br />\n食d咁Ge food<br />\n不如去屌個譚食個大快活la<br />\n$45食得飽😋😋"},{"pid":"768ddf612df63a402f790145afb3754baf57a009","tid":1014841,"uid":134665,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"又偷人野"},{"pid":"7d03